data.text:
Poultrygeist: Night of the Chicken Dead

When the American Chicken Bunker, a military-themed fast food restaurant, builds its latest chain restaurant on the site of an ancient Native American burial ground, the haunting spirits take revenge on the diners and transform them into chicken zombies! How would this foul-feathered nightmare end?
